anything more, Your Majesty.

57
00:06:14,050 --> 00:06:15,990
At this point of time

58
00:06:20,080 --> 00:06:22,890
may the Lord motivate you!

59
00:06:34,050 --> 00:06:36,050
This is my blessing.

60
