183
00:19:08,940 --> 00:19:11,820
when you have the opportunity

184
00:19:11,880 --> 00:19:15,720
of fulfilling the vow
of your teacher.

185
00:19:21,910 --> 00:19:24,750
Who will be able
to pay me my fees?

186
